            <title>[FLUME-2014] Race condition when using local timestamp with BucketPath</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLUME-2014</link>
                <project id="12311321" key="FLUME">Flume</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is a race condition in the BucketPath code logic which was exposed by adding local (non-event) timestamp capability to BucketPath and HDFS sink.&lt;/p&gt;

